it might give you a higher median damage vs equal level opponents? it didnt do much when i was playing. if the + envenom bonus was changed,then you would have to change the entire line  of poisons,and how they work, they would have to be much more open ended on either side,or change how the bonus skill works so that lower level poisons actually increase damage beyond what they can currently do.<br>
